item.title: #HackTheSolarSystem
item.description: Last weekend I had the opportunity to participate in my first ever hackathon: the #HackTheSolarSystem hackathon hosted by the American Museum of Natural History. What is a hackathon, anyways? This is a question I got asked countless times this last week as I informed my friends and family that I would be at work all weekend (yes, including Friday night, yes, including Saturday night, no, I will not be able to socialize at all).
